1
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:29,660
♪In the stormy night♪

2
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:37,340
♪The dark hair of a charming woman
is reflected in the flame of a candle♪

3
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:41,300
♪Shrouded by year after year
of memories♪

4
00:00:41,980 --> 00:00:45,780
♪I can do nothing
but feign indifference♪

5
00:00:46,220 --> 00:00:53,140
♪Outlining your cheeks♪

6
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:55,540
♪Together and apart,
just like quicksand♪

7
00:00:55,740 --> 00:00:57,420
♪I'm meant to make peace with myself♪

8
00:00:57,660 --> 00:01:01,140
♪Rebuild or crumble♪

9
00:01:01,420 --> 00:01:03,780
♪Drift away in the clouds♪

10
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:05,660
♪Driving away♪

11
00:01:06,020 --> 00:01:09,300
♪Your dashing pretense♪

12
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:11,620
♪A drunken dream♪

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:13,500
♪A person I miss♪

14
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:16,860
♪Of course I know if it's real♪

15
00:01:17,060 --> 00:01:21,660
♪Even if you're just by my side♪

16
00:01:22,180 --> 00:01:28,220
♪I want to hold on to you
but I can only play dumb♪

17
00:01:29,940 --> 00:01:35,060
[In Blossom]

18
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:38,740
[Episode 25]

19
00:01:42,270 --> 00:01:42,800
Master.

20
00:01:43,910 --> 00:01:46,360
Her Highness has entered the palace
to meet Her Majesty today.

21
00:01:46,910 --> 00:01:48,440
Pan Yue will be
transferred back to the capital.

22
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:51,230
After he finished investigating Heyang,

23
00:01:51,590 --> 00:01:52,630
he is now

24
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:55,040
trying to investigate me
here in the capital.

25
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:58,120
We didn't leave any trails in Heyang.

26
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,630
I don't think he knows

27
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,190
Zhuo Shanju worked for you.

28
00:02:03,310 --> 00:02:05,270
What can a kid do

29
00:02:05,630 --> 00:02:07,630
to stir trouble?

30
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,030
Go and make some arrangements,

31
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:11,320
so he is kept busy

32
00:02:11,830 --> 00:02:13,270
when he returns to the capital.

33
00:02:13,390 --> 00:02:13,750
All right.

34
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,240
Third Lane of Willow Street.

35
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:19,800
After we send ladies
into the capital every year,

36
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:21,670
they would put us

37
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:23,030
in a house there.

38
00:02:24,270 --> 00:02:25,910
When the ladies
had groomed themselves well,

39
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,520
they would pick them up

40
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,320
after they examined the ladies.

41
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:32,160
All right. Go before me.

42
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:34,000
When I finish handing over
matters at the county yamen,

43
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,750
I'll meet you in the capital.

44
00:02:36,830 --> 00:02:37,440
All right.

45
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:40,150
I will send someone
to the entrance of the street.

46
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:41,360
Carry a red umbrella

47
00:02:41,830 --> 00:02:43,110
and someone will pick you up.

48
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:44,720
All right.

49
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:48,080
Mr. Pan, be extra careful.

50
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:50,920
The grudge of the ladies
at Hundred Flowers Court

51
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,360
is in your hands.

52
00:02:54,830 --> 00:02:56,550
I will do my best.

53
00:02:56,550 --> 00:02:57,750
[Court]

54
00:02:57,750 --> 00:02:59,770
Convey His Majesty's decree.

55
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:02,160
Heyang's government has good integrity.

56
00:03:02,470 --> 00:03:04,270
Every department
is doing its duty diligently.

57
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:08,320
The magistrate, Pan Yue, is hardworking,
responsible, and favored by the people.

58
00:03:08,670 --> 00:03:09,320
From today onward,

59
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:13,270
Pan Yue will resign as the magistrate
of Heyang and return to the capital.

60
00:03:14,110 --> 00:03:16,240
I accept.

61
00:03:24,670 --> 00:03:25,910
Mr. Pan's return to the capital

62
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:28,110
must be due to a promotion.

63
00:03:28,270 --> 00:03:30,440
Let me congratulate you in advance.

64
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:32,390
Thank you, Mr. Wang.

65
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,670
Farewell.

66
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,440
Congratulations, sir.

67
00:03:48,750 --> 00:03:50,030
Come. Put down the fish.

68
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:51,630
Here. Hurry!

69
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,080
Go to the kitchen

70
00:03:53,110 --> 00:03:54,030
and bring the cutlery sets!

71
00:03:54,550 --> 00:03:55,320
Quick!

72
00:03:55,550 --> 00:03:56,030
Hurry up!

73
00:03:56,470 --> 00:03:57,800
The banquet will begin soon. Come here!

74
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,550
Put them here!

75
00:03:58,830 --> 00:03:59,550
Put them down!

76
00:04:00,910 --> 00:04:01,670
Hurry!

77
00:04:01,830 --> 00:04:03,600
Put the wine there, hurry!

78
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:10,630
Here. Quick!

79
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,640
Miss Shangguan,

80
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,160
to be honest,

81
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:21,790
I looked down on you

82
00:04:21,950 --> 00:04:22,880
at first.

83
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,070
A girl like you

84
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:26,480
chasing a man to the yamen.

85
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:27,790
It's ridiculous.

86
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:28,720
How absurd!

87
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:30,510
However,

88
00:04:31,230 --> 00:04:33,920
I've been impressed
after getting along with you.

89
00:04:34,790 --> 00:04:36,760
A girl learning to become a coroner

90
00:04:37,350 --> 00:04:38,670
is on par

91
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:39,760
with someone as experienced as me.

92
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:42,040
I'm ashamed.

93
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:44,390
If it wasn't for the very
first coroner's blessing, I...

94
00:04:45,110 --> 00:04:46,920
Right. I'm not qualified
for the position.

95
00:04:48,110 --> 00:04:49,640
Well, let me toast you.

96
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:50,320
Here.

97
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:53,600
Constable Liu.

98
00:04:54,230 --> 00:04:55,350
After I leave,

99
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:56,760
I'm sure you will feel relieved.

100
00:04:57,230 --> 00:04:57,920
In the future,

101
00:04:58,270 --> 00:04:59,920
no one will punish you anymore.

102
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:01,950
Not at all, sir.

103
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:03,600
I sincerely think

104
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,720
you should have been here sooner.

105
00:05:06,230 --> 00:05:07,440
I think

106
00:05:07,550 --> 00:05:09,040
I should have been punished sooner.

107
00:05:10,230 --> 00:05:11,760
Before you came to Heyang,

108
00:05:12,010 --> 00:05:14,200
we might be officials of the court,

109
00:05:15,110 --> 00:05:17,720
but we couldn't do anything.

110
00:05:17,950 --> 00:05:19,790
We dared not do anything.

111
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:24,070
We were just muddling away
by deceiving everyone.

112
00:05:24,790 --> 00:05:26,640
People of the Four Greats

113
00:05:26,790 --> 00:05:29,230
treated us like watchdogs.

114
00:05:29,830 --> 00:05:32,230
The people looked down on us.

115
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,160
After you came,

116
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:36,640
the county yamen
became a real county yamen.

117
00:05:37,110 --> 00:05:40,670
We investigated cases together
and punished the bad people.

118
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:43,830
Right now, we are proud

119
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,720
to wear our uniform.

120
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:48,950
This is all thanks to you, sir.

121
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:49,950
That's right.

122
00:05:50,070 --> 00:05:52,200
- It's all thanks to you, sir.
- Yes.

123
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,350
Everyone.

124
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,600
I came here

125
00:05:56,790 --> 00:05:57,950
to take this position temporarily.

126
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:01,600
However, Heyang is still your home.

127
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:03,670
Even if I resign now,

128
00:06:04,110 --> 00:06:06,720
I also hope
you all can protect your home

129
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,600
like you do right now.

130
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:12,320
Return true peace to Heyang.

131
00:06:13,110 --> 00:06:13,670
Here.

132
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,070
To everyone.

133
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:16,760
Sir, don't worry.

134
00:06:17,070 --> 00:06:20,000
All of us will never disappoint you.

135
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,320
I didn't expect Constable Liu
and Coroner Chen

136
00:06:28,550 --> 00:06:30,600
to change so much after a few months.

137
00:06:32,270 --> 00:06:34,110
Constable Liu was passionate
in the past,

138
00:06:35,230 --> 00:06:36,510
but those
who investigated cases seriously

139
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:38,110
couldn't survive here.

140
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,040
He gradually became the way he was

141
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,510
to take care of his family.

142
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,640
The environment changes people.

143
00:06:46,110 --> 00:06:48,720
One will go crazy or be dead
if they do something against the group.

144
00:06:49,550 --> 00:06:50,200
Yes.

145
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,200
Master became mad

146
00:06:53,110 --> 00:06:54,720
and you almost died.

147
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:57,070
I came back to find you previously,

148
00:06:58,110 --> 00:07:00,160
but I didn't expect you
to experience all this.

149
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,000
I don't regret everything
that happened in the past.

150
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,600
Thank you for coming.

151
00:07:07,270 --> 00:07:08,480
Thank you for finding me.

152
00:07:13,340 --> 00:07:16,460
♪Clouds painted by flying geese♪

153
00:07:19,230 --> 00:07:20,110
Wait for me.

154
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:25,920
Wait for me.

155
00:07:27,300 --> 00:07:30,180
♪You are the beginning♪

156
00:07:31,740 --> 00:07:36,020
♪Even if I don't care about our love♪

157
00:07:36,260 --> 00:07:40,660
♪You're still the remnant
of a line I'm trying to complete♪

158
00:07:41,060 --> 00:07:45,260
♪Even if I don't mention the past♪

159
00:07:49,110 --> 00:07:50,390
I was wondering
why I haven't seen it for so long.

160
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:51,830
It turned out that you threw it away.

161
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,390
You had the princess back then.

162
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,670
Why would I want to keep it?

163
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,440
I didn't throw it away

164
00:07:57,510 --> 00:07:58,510
when you were flirting with Jiang.

165
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:00,040
Are you blaming me now?

166
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,000
Why would I?

167
00:08:04,550 --> 00:08:05,110
I...

168
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,390
Just don't want them
to be separated anymore.

169
00:08:11,940 --> 00:08:13,220
[Good]

170
00:08:32,590 --> 00:08:33,960
Have you determined the price

171
00:08:34,550 --> 00:08:35,670
for the things I want to pawn?

172
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,030
Sir.

173
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:42,320
Someone sent a note.

174
00:08:47,710 --> 00:08:49,470
Someone is interested in your items.

175
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,470
Go to this place.

176
00:08:58,500 --> 00:08:59,940
[Hongfu Restaurant]

177
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:41,340
[Good quality items at a cheap price]

178
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:48,320
Why are you following me?

179
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:54,080
I've come to this street to see
if there's a suitable stall.

180
00:09:54,150 --> 00:09:55,150
I want to start a business.

181
00:10:01,150 --> 00:10:03,400
What do you want? Tell me.

182
00:10:03,470 --> 00:10:04,640
What if I can help you?

183
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,030
Stop following me.

184
00:10:11,230 --> 00:10:12,520
Otherwise, don't blame me
for being rude.

185
00:10:13,350 --> 00:10:14,030
Stop!

186
00:10:14,150 --> 00:10:16,200
Holding a sharp weapon
and threatening a lady

187
00:10:16,280 --> 00:10:17,710
in the light of day.

188
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:19,110
I'll report to the officials
if you don't stop!

189
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:20,000
Exactly!

190
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,110
What's wrong with you?

191
00:10:21,150 --> 00:10:22,550
Trying to murder someone in the day?

192
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:23,710
She's a lady no less.

193
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:24,440
This is too much!

194
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,230
Exactly.

195
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:26,790
That's right.

196
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:29,030
What is he doing?

197
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:31,400
Stop!

198
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,110
Stop!

199
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,230
Move.

200
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:33,960
No!

201
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:35,080
This is the capital.

202
00:10:35,110 --> 00:10:36,080
How dare you do as you wish

203
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,550
under His Majesty's rule.

204
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:38,880
- That's right!
- Indeed!

205
00:10:38,970 --> 00:10:40,090
- Who is he?
- How can we let you leave?

206
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:41,590
Stop! You can't leave!

207
00:10:41,670 --> 00:10:43,550
Well, we know each other.

208
00:10:43,590 --> 00:10:44,910
We were just fooling around.

209
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,110
Fooling around?

210
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:47,400
Do you really know him?

211
00:10:47,470 --> 00:10:48,280
I do.

212
00:10:49,350 --> 00:10:50,200
Thank you.

213
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:52,030
They know each other. Let's go.

214
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:52,680
Ignore them.

215
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:55,310
- Let's go.
- They made us look like busybodies.

216
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,880
Stop following me in the future.

217
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:05,260
[Hongfu Restaurant]

218
00:11:27,230 --> 00:11:29,200
You go and cause trouble
at the pawn shop every day.

219
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:31,760
What are you trying to do?

220
00:11:35,590 --> 00:11:37,790
My father worked for you
all through his life.

221
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:38,880
In the end,

222
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:43,230
his reputation was ruined,
and he died a cruel death.

223
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,000
Tell me.

224
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:48,440
What do you think I want to do?

225
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:52,760
You are here to get money
for his funeral.

226
00:11:53,590 --> 00:11:54,590
I want to know

227
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:57,150
for whom he was doing all of these.

228
00:11:58,520 --> 00:11:59,710
I want to complete

229
00:12:00,460 --> 00:12:01,900
the things he hadn't completed.

230
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,110
Just you alone?

231
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,840
You are also following orders.

232
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:17,840
You are not the one

233
00:12:18,230 --> 00:12:19,790
to judge whether I am qualified
to do this or not.

234
00:12:30,110 --> 00:12:31,230
Do you see that man over there?

235
00:12:32,550 --> 00:12:34,710
Mr. Zhang,
congratulations on your promotion.

236
00:12:34,910 --> 00:12:35,790
We share the joy.

237
00:12:39,710 --> 00:12:41,080
Kill him in three days.

238
00:12:42,470 --> 00:12:43,960
Then, Master will see you.

239
00:12:49,700 --> 00:12:54,940
[Luoyi]

240
00:13:08,470 --> 00:13:12,280
- Bravo!
- Nice one!

241
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:18,320
Many shops are different now
compared to the past.

242
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:19,910
When I left the capital a decade ago,

243
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,910
my parents
and I were going on this road.

244
00:13:23,710 --> 00:13:25,280
Unfortunately,
they died in another place

245
00:13:25,550 --> 00:13:26,550
and never returned.

246
00:13:28,350 --> 00:13:29,400
We return to the capital this time

247
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,710
to find the mastermind

248
00:13:32,350 --> 00:13:34,080
and appease your parents' spirits.

249
00:13:51,150 --> 00:13:53,350
Where is Mr. Pan Yue?

250
00:14:00,230 --> 00:14:01,000
I am Pan Yue.

251
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:03,840
I'm here to welcome you
according to His Majesty's order.

252
00:14:05,350 --> 00:14:06,000
Please wait.

253
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:11,960
There's no need to worry.

254
00:14:12,350 --> 00:14:13,520
I think
I need to be appointed in the palace.

255
00:14:13,880 --> 00:14:15,280
I'll ask Ze
to send you back to the residence.

256
00:14:15,550 --> 00:14:16,470
I'll come to you later.

257
00:14:16,670 --> 00:14:17,640
Be careful.

258
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:21,440
Let's go.

259
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:42,200
Young Lady.

260
00:14:45,910 --> 00:14:46,590
Zhi.

261
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:49,440
Lan...

262
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:51,400
Zhi.

263
00:14:52,030 --> 00:14:53,520
Did you know how much I've missed you

264
00:14:54,400 --> 00:14:55,880
after all these days?

265
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:59,520
I've missed you too, Lan.

266
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:01,840
Let me see.

267
00:15:03,470 --> 00:15:04,910
You haven't changed much.

268
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:08,400
You seem to be in better health.

269
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:13,520
What's wrong?

270
00:15:14,520 --> 00:15:15,790
You are acting like a stranger

271
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:17,470
even if it hasn't been long
since we last met.

272
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:19,000
No.

273
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,280
Not at all.

274
00:15:21,110 --> 00:15:23,640
A younger sister avoids her brother
when she grows up.

275
00:15:23,710 --> 00:15:25,030
Stop treating me like a child

276
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:26,590
in front of so many people.

277
00:15:27,110 --> 00:15:28,080
You are right, Zhi.

278
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,320
You've grown up indeed.

279
00:15:29,470 --> 00:15:29,960
Let's go.

280
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:38,350
Baocai.

