580
00:31:08,230 --> 00:31:09,520
She has always been hostile towards you.

581
00:31:11,800 --> 00:31:13,230
After you left for some time,

582
00:31:13,280 --> 00:31:15,430
you look so much better.

583
00:31:16,590 --> 00:31:18,590
Look at your skin and body.

584
00:31:18,880 --> 00:31:20,040
Even the Jade Rabbit

585
00:31:20,040 --> 00:31:22,190
