586
00:31:23,430 --> 00:31:25,000
You too.

587
00:31:25,470 --> 00:31:26,400
Let's go, Zhi.

588
00:31:26,520 --> 00:31:28,070
Join me in drinking tea
and watching flowers.

589
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:29,470
