601
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:05,800
summoned Pan Jin and his son

602
00:32:06,040 --> 00:32:07,000
to give the wedding invitation.

603
00:32:08,070 --> 00:32:09,560
On the 15th day of the next month,

604
00:32:10,040 --> 00:32:11,590
Pan Yue will marry the princess

605
00:32:12,830 --> 00:32:14,230
according to Her Majesty's decree.

606
00:32:15,800 --> 00:32:16,640
What did you say?

607
00:32:17,110 --> 00:32:18,160
Zhi,

608
00:32:18,520 --> 00:32:20,070
did you really not know?

609
00:32:22,810 --> 00:32:25,110
You went after Pan Yue

610
00:32:25,230 --> 00:32:27,160
to a barren place like Heyang,

611
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:30,280
but he still abandoned you.

612
00:32:31,350 --> 00:32:33,280
I feel sorry for you.

613
00:32:35,920 --> 00:32:37,230
Is she telling the truth?

614
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:38,940
There hasn't been any news

615
00:32:38,940 --> 00:32:40,040
since Pan Yue
entered the palace yesterday.

616
00:32:40,390 --> 00:32:41,670
Is it because of this?

617
00:32:42,640 --> 00:32:44,280
Your family is so rich.
If Pan Yue marries someone else,

618
00:32:44,350 --> 00:32:46,640
you can just add some dowry

619
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:48,470
to become his concubine.

620
00:32:48,560 --> 00:32:50,070
That might work

621
00:32:50,350 --> 00:32:51,470
thanks to your family's assets.

622
00:32:52,470 --> 00:32:54,710
However, he's going
to marry the princess.

623
00:32:55,070 --> 00:32:58,280
The princess
will never agree to share her husband

624
00:32:58,640 --> 00:33:00,000
with a merchant's daughter.

625
00:33:00,680 --> 00:33:02,000
A person needs to know

626
00:33:02,040 --> 00:33:03,520
what's best for them.

627
00:33:03,760 --> 00:33:06,110
What a shame that she wasted
so many years of her youth

628
00:33:06,230 --> 00:33:08,230
