658
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:23,150
You mustn't reject it.

659
00:34:23,230 --> 00:34:24,360
You must accept it.

660
00:34:24,430 --> 00:34:25,950
I have a lot of this in my residence.
You use it.

661
00:34:25,950 --> 00:34:27,280
Zhi, just take it.

662
00:34:27,430 --> 00:34:28,230
Use it.

663
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:29,320
I also have a lot.

664
00:34:29,390 --> 00:34:30,230
You must use it.

665
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:31,120
Zhi.

666
00:34:44,870 --> 00:34:45,230
This...

667
00:34:45,760 --> 00:34:46,390
You...

668
00:34:57,470 --> 00:34:58,360
Don't come after me!

669
00:34:59,040 --> 00:35:00,320
Don't come after me!

670
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:04,150
