678
00:35:22,910 --> 00:35:23,870
How preposterous.

679
00:35:24,630 --> 00:35:26,190
Is she the princess?

680
00:35:28,430 --> 00:35:29,840
Are you Shangguan Zhi?

681
00:35:31,630 --> 00:35:32,560
Your face

682
00:35:32,710 --> 00:35:34,190
is different from what I imagined.

683
00:35:36,310 --> 00:35:36,990
What a coincidence.

684
00:35:37,230 --> 00:35:39,080
I have something to ask you about Pan.

685
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:39,910
Come with me.

686
00:35:57,800 --> 00:35:58,800
Shangguan Zhi,

687
00:35:58,910 --> 00:36:00,430
I'll see how long
you can keep acting so arrogantly.

688
00:36:02,630 --> 00:36:04,120
Her Highness,
I wonder what you want to know

689
00:36:04,230 --> 00:36:05,280
by bringing me here.

690
00:36:05,950 --> 00:36:07,630
I'm still waiting for someone,

691
00:36:08,320 --> 00:36:08,910
so...

692
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:09,910
Are you waiting for Pan?

693
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,760
Pan and I are discussing
something important,

694
00:36:17,120 --> 00:36:18,840
