718
00:37:18,150 --> 00:37:20,390
If you are a reasonable person
who is able to see the bigger picture,

719
00:37:20,870 --> 00:37:22,390
you should let him return to his place

720
00:37:22,840 --> 00:37:24,430
and not hinder his future.

721
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:25,840
Am I right?

722
00:37:29,760 --> 00:37:31,390
Your Highness' words might be right,

723
00:37:32,430 --> 00:37:34,080
