724
00:37:36,150 --> 00:37:38,560
When men fall in love, they can
get away from it whenever they want.

725
00:37:38,910 --> 00:37:41,280
When women fall in love,
they are infatuated.

726
00:37:42,310 --> 00:37:44,190
Miss Yang, you are too confident.

727
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:48,230
